overview:
HahaCouponCodes is a shopping and money saving website listing all the latest deals and discounts from Indian stores.

The site distributes a weekly newsletter, which features a selection of the twenty best coupon codes for a huge range of stores and activities.

HahaCouponCodes covers a wide range of products in over 9 product categories including restaurants, hotels, travel, and all popular shopping categories like clothes, footwear, books, computers, electronics, furniture, education, food, gifts, health, beauty, Jewellery,games, toys, music & movies etc.
